### Session Document Reference
- ALWAYS include explicit reference to current session document
- Format: `docs/sessions/YYYY-MM-DD-description.md`
- Include brief description of what's in the session doc

### Cleanup
- Delete any previous `HANDOVER*.md` files
- Keep only the current `HANDOVER.md`
- Do NOT create multiple handover files

### When User Says
- "Create a handover" ‚Üí Create `HANDOVER.md`
- "Refresh context" ‚Üí Create `HANDOVER.md`
- "Handover prompt" ‚Üí Create `HANDOVER.md`
