### Documentation Updates Before Handover
1. Update session document with progress
2. Update ARCHITECTURE.md if new components added
3. Update DEVELOPMENT.md if new processes/tests added
4. Update CHANGELOG.md with changes
5. THEN create HANDOVER.md

